{"tid":438711,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 遊戲王 duel links(37) 電子雞世代（玩撚完）","createTime":"2017-10-17T07:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T07:56:30.000Z","uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"755634392540c1bb782df8091249fd79d3cbe90b","tid":438711,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:44:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">洗唔洗刷首抽</span><br />\n唔洗，個box啲卡限死數量，終有一日會抽晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解個場得三格/點解deck限20-30張卡</span><br />\n本遊戲採取快速決鬥規則<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點拎角色</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.isheart.com/archives/4433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.isheart.com%2Farchives%2F4433&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9ksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=f992a6fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.isheart.com/archives/4433</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">啲卡點拎</span><br />\n分別有<br />\n角色等級獎勵<br />\n卡片商人 (stage7 unlock)<br />\n路人掉落<br />\n打Gate<br />\n同埋抽卡包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咩叫Reset 卡包</span><br />\n抽完/抽中目標物之後 可以reset卡包重頭抽過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">新手請用海馬起手</span></span><br />\n然後抽海馬個套牌500石抽曬20張卡<br />\n隻1700攻龍配海馬4lv個場地技變1900攻<br />\n海馬好d係因為兩個套牌中嘅卡實用d<br />\n同埋好多有用嘅龍族可以係高lv d會解鎖嘅商人買到  幻影龍  龍之尖兵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新手抽邊個卡包好</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以先抽有高攻怪R卡既卡然後就跟下面咁上下抽  主要都係睇自己點組<br />\n鳳凰神&gt;究極龍&gt;天使=混沌士兵=暴君龍&gt;流星黑龍&gt;吸血鬼&gt;沉默&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;XYZ&gt;鳥獸&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;獸包<br />\n水包可以抽下r卡食人魚(水DECK主要卡都係商人買.)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點set技能</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/13/110027_99ac597844832fc8b37f05deb821e538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F13%2F110027_99ac597844832fc8b37f05deb821e538.jpg&h=325aa7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Quiz點打</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=29618&amp;snB=318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FCo.php%3Fbsn%3D29618%26snB%3D318&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9ksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2fde7026\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=29618&amp;snB=318</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">打Gate有咩要注意</span><br />\n除左解任之外儲key先<br />\n等到unlock lv40先去刷卡刷技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">結算分點計</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u2dtrpnz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu2dtrpnz&h=6c55a497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點樣刷到高分</span><br />\n魔導獸deck<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=J5cN0TBKmWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshared%3Fci%3DJ5cN0TBKmWE&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9ksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2c88063e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=J5cN0TBKmWE</a><br />\n打法係堆攻擊力過一萬同壓血<br />\n（其實一隻魔導獸都得）<br />\n*<span style=\"color: gold;\">只刷到部分角色</span><br />\n<br />\n薄幸乙女deck<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SCSOXqZsPz4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSCSOXqZsPz4&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9ksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2f731bcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SCSOXqZsPz4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咩叫派小智/流浪者/神秘人/紅帽 etc</span><br />\n係你加左好友之後<br />\n有時打完佢會問你有冇朋友介紹，同埋要set咩challenge 俾佢<br />\n揀一張卡起手就啱架啦，超過二千經驗值<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">免費石呀！！！</span></span><br />\n點觸遊戲介面以下地方可獲得數量1、3、5顆不等的石頭。<br />\n1.噴水池：出現噴水彩虹<br />\n2.街燈：發出彩虹光<br />\n3.商店上方卡片：出現禮物汽球<br />\n4.垃圾桶：出現強慾之壺<br />\n獲得一定時間過後可再次點觸獲得。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Duellinks卡表網</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.korekara.url.tw/yogioh/deck/deck.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.korekara.url.tw%2Fyogioh%2Fdeck%2Fdeck.html&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9ksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6564a8d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.korekara.url.tw/yogioh/deck/deck.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">參考兼攻略網</span><br />\n英文<a href=\"http://duellinks.gamea.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fduellinks.gamea.co%2F&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9ksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=8e633b36\" target=\"_blank\">http://duellinks.gamea.co/</a><br />\n日文<a href=\"https://duellinks.gamewith.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fduellinks.gamewith.jp%2F&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9ksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2477c5b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://duellinks.gamewith.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i68.tinypic.com/2epswoh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi68.tinypic.com%2F2epswoh.jpg&h=81720091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一屆連登盃</span></strong></span>(規則 30張卡 技能:重新開始 禁自閉DECK)<br />\n冠軍 LRLRLRLRLRLRLR<br />\n亞軍 飲水絲源<br />\n季軍 法國光頭佬<br />\n殿軍 weshito"},{"pid":"0bd14d9d4acc9763ade7db0d6ad42439c6e241fd","tid":438711,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:46:18.000Z","msg":"請過電子雞已死個POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc25498d5d3adf0201c5cba481b179fc1d49e8f","tid":438711,"uid":73406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"K社最仆街係搞個舊包優惠，一完就限咗儀式，限看破又係唔用腦，白龍deck玩完"},{"pid":"7c04f88404fabc0e6e8bdf80019a213b3d91ceef","tid":438711,"uid":42330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:46:53.000Z","ms